snippet.title: Oddworld: Soulstorm Enhanced Edition Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Oddworld: Soulstorm Enhanced Edition is coming to PlayStation, Xbox and Epic Games Store 11.30.21.

Pre-Order now for Xbox Series S | X and Xbox One
UK: https://www.xbox.com/en-gb/games/store/oddworld-soulstorm-enhanced-edition/9n2xhrdkcjpg
US: https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/oddworld-soulstorm-enhanced-edition/9n2xhrdkcjpg

Sign up for all the latest news and info at www.oddworld.com

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/OfficialOddworld/
